0930ec26cff7709","tid":360008,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢做教師有幾多係講熱誠同責任?<br />\n十居其九都係為左搵食，hae 做<br />\n唔畀佢地上位係避免佢地進化成教畜"},{"pid":"c3e9f6576f215571052cb6fda02a722c097edbe5","tid":360008,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T05:41:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個時勢做教師有幾多係講熱誠同責任?<br />\n十居其九都係為左搵食，hae 做<br />\n唔畀佢地上位係避免佢地進化成教畜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你好教畜"},{"pid":"18375268ef0ef79f32a42947489c30648545d8bd","tid":360008,"uid":89441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T06:30:04.000Z","msg":"又真係幾sad ，中五、六個年有個教通識既阿sir幾好，全級學生都幾鍾意佢，點知教左兩年之後走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多當年教過我既老師都唔係度，間中學變得好陌生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076302e3bd08613ed1f263171b14fa00d87c6894","tid":360008,"uid":23469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其他行業都係行合約制架啦</blockquote><br />\n合約係大勢所趨，唔明點解教師叫春叫得特別勁，覺得自己高人一等，覺得唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係大勢所趨就等於合理。</blockquote><br />\n無話合理，只係教師叫春特別勁</blockquote><br />\n應該全部轉晒合約制就真<br />\n一轉長工 成班教畜就變hea 咩鳩都俾晒contract做<br />\n幾懶幾hea都冇人炒到佢地<br />\n最好全部都係合約制 年年review 淘汰班hea/廢人 增加競爭<br />\n咁就對學生最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26301d208dbf44e1d99950610037b902cc57f226","tid":360008,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T06:47:55.000Z","msg":"年年咁多教書既畢業 你估重咁馨香咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出生率又低 自己要既老師又少左<br />\n<br />\n第時用埋電子化教學 老師都唔洗請呀 請個ta就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各行各業都有階級觀念 唔係淨係得老師呢一行</span>"},{"pid":"98b01773889b097eca661726046f3ce65679724c","tid":360008,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T06:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其他行業都係行合約制架啦</blockquote><br />\n合約係大勢所趨，唔明點解教師叫春叫得特別勁，覺得自己高人一等，覺得唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係大勢所趨就等於合理。</blockquote><br />\n無話合理，只係教師叫春特別勁</blockquote><br />\n畢因為覺得自己死讀爛讀 諗住做份好工<br />\n點知入職半年就要搵定下間<br />\n覺得唔服埋叫春囉"},{"pid":"c63ed36c48e8488fc800e83e307c7434c4658a3e","tid":360008,"uid":54875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"唔應該加常額教席<br />\n應該cut哂全部常額轉合約制<br />\n等班老屎忽唔敢蝦蝦霸霸<br />\n教育界作育英才好應該能者居之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5105c9c775a06173fb23a744c827cdd757d7c9a3","tid":360008,"uid":41382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"而家行行都行合約架啦"},{"pid":"9c6d52c150b41c69fd681cc39a6f5b05794ffcca","tid":360008,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T09:47:43.000Z","msg":"做工程尊嚴又係邊？"},{"pid":"92b771c90bc82e706f901202aa89b61bc942a365","tid":360008,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"咁仆街分兩個教員室坐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}